**Herding Dog** | Solo Power - Flock Team | Limited
__Basics__
The Herding Dog wins with the shepherd and joins a channel with the shepherd to communicate securely.
The Herding Dog can choose to communicate securely with a herded player each night.
The Herding Dog can also infiltrate the Herded channel in place of another player being herded
__Details__
Each night the Herding Dog can choose a herded player and add them to a seperate channel to anonymously communicate with them
The Herding Dog can also choose to become herded in place of another person that night, while herded the Herding Dog becomes immune to attacks like other herded players
